From: Adrian Alonso <aalonso@freescale.com>
Date: Mon, 12 Oct 2015 14:10:25 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 0956/1691] MLK-11696-1: arm: dts: imx7d iomuxc-lpsr add fsl
 input select property

commit a813088e91ee14e2083dcd128525343e5b0037d4 from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_4.1.15_1.0.0_ga

Add iomuxc-lpsr fsl,input-sel property for shared input select
support, insteand of parsing the device tree on iomuxc probe
function to get iomuxc base address this property helps to
identify when shared input select register is needed.

Signed-off-by: Adrian Alonso <aalonso@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Robin Gong <b38343@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d.dtsi | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d.dtsi
index 92a010d..ca57867 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d.dtsi
@@ -512,6 +512,7 @@
 			iomuxc_lpsr: iomuxc-lpsr@302c0000 {
 				compatible = "fsl,imx7d-iomuxc-lpsr";
 				reg = <0x302c0000 0x10000>;
+				fsl,input-sel = <&iomuxc>;
 			};
 
 			gpt1: gpt@302d0000 {
